Quickstrike:






Quickstrike, now being back on the solid ground, caught himself on a near-by 
sapling. His body wasn't going to support him much longer. If a new bots saw 
him now, with no explaination of his condition, they would think he was 
drunk.

"Easy," he said to Sinesis. "Go inside. The computer will let ya in," he 
guestured a long fingered hand to him. "if ya ask 'er." He looked to the 
ship. "Computer, on-guard. Prepare fer enemy attack. Fire auto-guns on any 
unknown Predacon signatures." He named all the Predacons on Hell Beast's 
team as best as he could, then as he was finished, he stepped forward. He 
whimpered at the pain in his leg. It wouldn't let him go any further.
